M. Dzurinda, poslanec: }{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
P\u225\'e1n poslanec, pod\u318\'3ea m\u244\'f4jho n\u225\'e1zoru za oby\u269\'0dajn\u233\'e9 fr\u225\'e1zy schov\u225\'e1vate neschopnos\u357\'65 rie\u353\'61i\u357\'65 p\u225\'e1l\u269\'0div\u233\'e9 probl\u233\'e9my ob\u269\'0danov Slovenskej republiky, oby\u269\'0dajn\u253\'fdch \u318\'3eud\u237\'ed, ktor\u237\'ed si chc\u250\'fa udr\u382\'7ea\u357\'65 pr\u225\'e1cu. Ukazujete st\u225\'e1le viac svoju absol\u250\'fatnu neschopnos\u357\'65 \u269\'0deli\u357\'65 t\u253\'fdmto v\u225\'e1\u382\'7enym probl\u233\'e9mom, \u269\'0deli\u357\'65 prep\u250\'fa\u353\'61\u357\'65aniu, rast\u250\'facej nezamestnanosti. Urobili ste tu ak\u253\'fdsi exkurz, v ktorom ste pojedn\u225\'e1vali o benefitoch bohat\u253\'fdch alebo chudobn\u253\'fdch, ak prijmeme n\u225\'e1vrh, ktor\u253\'fd predniesol kolega Miklo\u353\'61. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
Chcem sa v\u225\'e1s op\u253\'fdta\u357\'65, p\u225\'e1n poslanec. Je benefitom pre \u269\'0dloveka s n\u237\'edzkymi pr\u237\'edjmami, ak v\u271\'0faka tak\u253\'fdmto opatreniam stimuluj\u250\'facim ekonomiku, motivuj\u250\'facim podnikate\u318\'3esk\u233\'e9 prostredie, ak si tak\u253\'fdto robotn\u237\'edk udr\u382\'7e\u237\'ed pr\u225\'e1cu? Je to soci\u225\'e1lne alebo je nesoci\u225\'e1lne, ke\u271\'0f br\u225\'e1nite prij\u237\'edma\u357\'65 opatrenia, v\u271\'0faka ktor\u253\'fdm si aj \u318\'3eudia s n\u237\'edzkymi pr\u237\'edjmami m\u244\'f4\u382\'7eu udr\u382\'7ea\u357\'65 pr\u225\'e1cu alebo pr\u225\'e1cu n\u225\'e1js\u357\'65 a z\u237\'edska\u357\'65? Toto je va\u353\'61a solidarita? Br\u225\'e1ni\u357\'65 prij\u237\'edmaniu opatrenia alebo opatren\u237\'ed, aby \u318\'3eudia si udr\u382\'7eali robotu, aj t\u237\'ed, ktor\u237\'ed maj\u250\'fa najni\u382\'7e\u353\'61ie pr\u237\'edjmy?}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
O tom to cel\u233\'e9 je, p\u225\'e1n poslanec, o tomto to cel\u233\'e9 je. Tie fr\u225\'e1zy boli ve\u318\'3emi falo\u353\'61n\u233\'e9. Solidarita, ktor\u250\'fa hl\u225\'e1sate, povedie k \u271\'0fal\u353\'61iemu prep\u250\'fa\u353\'61\u357\'65aniu a k dokazovaniu, \u382\'7ee ste absol\u250\'fatne neschopn\u237\'ed rie\u353\'61i\u357\'65 probl\u233\'e9my oby\u269\'0dajn\u253\'fdch \u318\'3eud\u237\'ed.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
A e\u353\'61te jedna pozn\u225\'e1mka. Hovorili ste, \u382\'7ee rie\u353\'61ime probl\u233\'e9my od zelen\u233\'e9ho stola. Bolo to smutn\u233\'e9 v\u225\'e1s po\u269\'0d\u250\'fava\u357\'65, p\u225\'e1n poslanec. S kolegom Miklo\u353\'61om som tohto roku nav\u353\'61t\u237\'edvili asi 17 fabr\u237\'edk. Od Kechneca v priemyselnom parku cez Martin povedzme a\u382\'7e po Pova\u382\'7eie, kde sme boli v \u353\'61iestich fabrik\u225\'e1ch. V\u225\'e1\u353\'61 predseda vl\u225\'e1dy sa za\u353\'61il do Bratislavy, chod\u237\'ed len po kulo\u225\'e1roch, a ke\u271\'0f sa raz vyberie do ter\u233\'e9nu, aj to urob\u237\'ed \u8222\'1epr\u250\'fa\u353\'61vih\u8220\'1c ako v Opatovciach. (Potlesk a reakcie z pl\u233\'e9na.)}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30

