P. Fre\u353\'61o, poslanec: }{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
\u270\'0eakujem pekne, p\u225\'e1n predsedaj\u250\'faci. V\u225\'e1\u382\'7een\u253\'fd p\u225\'e1n kolega Petr\u225\'e1k, chcel by som v\u225\'e1m uk\u225\'e1za\u357\'65 in\u253\'fd poh\u318\'3ead na tento z\u225\'e1kon, nielen poh\u318\'3ead zo strany z\u225\'e1visti bohat\u253\'fdm vo\u269\'0di chudobn\u253\'fdm. Tak\u382\'7ee zn\u237\'ed\u382\'7eenie dan\u237\'ed m\u225\'e1 ten charakter, \u382\'7ee plat\u237\'ed aj pre firmy. A pokia\u318\'3e zn\u237\'ed\u382\'7eite da\u328\'48 pre firmy, tak sa dostanete do situ\u225\'e1cie, dostanete sa do situ\u225\'e1cie, kedy zn\u237\'ed\u382\'7een\u233\'e9 dane sp\u244\'f4sobia, \u382\'7ee firmy ostan\u250\'fa na Slovensku. To znamen\u225\'e1, \u382\'7ee naozaj t\u225\'e1 robota zostane na Slovensku a naozaj na Slovensku fabriky bud\u250\'fa m\u244\'f4c\u357\'65 zamestn\u225\'e1va\u357\'65 \u318\'3eud\u237\'ed. A pokia\u318\'3e si bud\u250\'fa m\u244\'f4c\u357\'65 vybra\u357\'65, pokia\u318\'3e si bud\u250\'fa m\u244\'f4c\u357\'65 vybra\u357\'65 \u318\'3eudia, alebo pokia\u318\'3e si bud\u250\'fa m\u244\'f4c\u357\'65 vybra\u357\'65 majite\u318\'3ea t\u253\'fdchto fabr\u237\'edk, tak ich nebud\u250\'fa umiest\u328\'48ova\u357\'65 do zahrani\u269\'0dia, ale bud\u250\'fa ich umiest\u328\'48ova\u357\'65 na Slovensku. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
