2\'7eitkova\u357\'65 \u269\'0drtaj\u250\'facu sa v\u228\'e4\u269\'0d\u353\'61iu flexibilitu v realiz\u225\'e1cii investorsk\u253\'fdch a obchodn\u253\'fdch z\u225\'e1merov vl\u225\'e1dy. Z h\u318\'3eadiska riadenia by nov\u225\'e1 in\u353\'61tit\u250\'facia bola podriaden\u225\'e1 vl\u225\'e1de, ktor\u225\'e1 by vymen\u250\'favala aj jeho riadiaci org\u225\'e1n. V tomto pr\u237\'edpade by do \u250\'favahy prich\u225\'e1dzala extern\u225\'e1 kontrola zo strany NK\u218\'da a \u218\'daradu vl\u225\'e1dy a tie\u382\'7e intern\u233\'e9 kontroly prostredn\u237\'edctvom Dozornej rady.}
