S. Jani\u353\'61, poslanec: }{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
Len kratu\u269\'0dk\u233\'e9 pozn\u225\'e1mky. P\u225\'e1n kolega, fond \u382\'7eije z vlastn\u253\'fdch zdrojov. No figu borov\u250\'fa! Z ak\u253\'fdch vlastn\u253\'fdch zdrojov? Fond n\u225\'e1rodn\u233\'e9ho majetku \u382\'7eije s nakladan\u237\'edm alebo naklad\u225\'e1 s majetkom \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tu, naklad\u225\'e1 s majetkom da\u328\'48ov\u253\'fdch poplatn\u237\'edkov. Fond n\u225\'e1rodn\u233\'e9ho majetku nie je s\u250\'fakromn\u225\'e1 firma, teda \u382\'7eije zo zdrojov \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tu da\u328\'48ov\u253\'fdch poplatn\u237\'edkov, tak\u382\'7ee nie z vlastn\u253\'fdch.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
K privatiz\u225\'e1cii. Ak by ste boli pokra\u269\'0dovali v privatiz\u225\'e1cii letiska, \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tny rozpo\u269\'0det by dostal 10 mld. kor\u250\'fan cash, 9 mld. by bolo, dnes z 9 mld. s\u318\'3e\u250\'faben\u253\'fdch invest\u237\'edci\u237\'ed by bolo 6 mld. investovan\u253\'fdch, bol by dnes nov\u253\'fd termin\u225\'e1l, prist\u225\'e1vacia dr\u225\'e1ha, parkovisk\u225\'e1, hotely. To, \u269\'0do m\u225\'e1me dnes, z Bratislavy u\u382\'7e nelieta nikto. Do Bruselu, kde chod\u237\'ed vl\u225\'e1da a N\u225\'e1rodn\u225\'e1 rada, poslanci, tak lietame v\u353\'61etci zo Schwechatu. To, \u269\'0do dok\u225\'e1zalo \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tne letisko, je postavi\u357\'65 stany.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
O Cargu v bledomodrom to ist\u233\'e9. Ak by ste boli sprivatizovali Cargo, dokon\u269\'0dili, tak by \u353\'61t\u225\'e1t dostal 13 mld. kor\u250\'fan cash plus 5 mld. preberal rak\u250\'fasky kupuj\u250\'faci. Cargo podvy\u382\'7eiven\u233\'e9 by bolo kapit\u225\'e1lovo posil\u328\'48oval, rak\u250\'faske Cargo, nov\u253\'fd investor by priniesol nov\u233\'e9 tovary na slovensk\u233\'e9 \u382\'7eeleznice, vtiahol by Cargo do medzin\u225\'e1rodn\u253\'fdch prepravn\u253\'fdch koridorov. Toto by bolo naozaj zlat\u233\'e9 vajce, ktor\u233\'e9 by prin\u225\'e1\u353\'61alo Cargu pr\u225\'e1cu a slovensk\u233\'e9mu \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tnemu rozpo\u269\'0dtu a slovensk\u253\'fdm ko\u318\'3eajniciam peniaze. To zlat\u233\'e9 vajce pod\u318\'3ea Roberta Fica dnes vyzer\u225\'e1 tak, \u382\'7ee rak\u250\'faske Cargo k\u250\'fapilo ma\u271\'0farsk\u233\'e9 Cargo, presmerovalo toky z v\u253\'fdchodu na z\u225\'e1pad na ma\u271\'0farsk\u233\'e9 ko\u318\'3eajnice, tr\u382\'7eby Carga klesaj\u250\'fa, \u353\'61t\u225\'e1t dnes sanuje Cargo 5 mld. kor\u250\'fan da\u328\'48ov\u253\'fdch poplatn\u237\'edkov. Toto je... (Preru\u353\'61enie vyst\u250\'fapenia \u269\'0dasomierou.)}
