\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
Fond n\u225\'e1rodn\u233\'e9ho majetku zamestn\u225\'e1va 110 zamestnancov, z toho 16 politick\u253\'fdch nominantov v Prez\u237\'eddiu a Dozornej rade, 11 riadite\u318\'3eov, 26 riadiacich pracovn\u237\'edkov, spolu n\u225\'e1klady 150 mil. kor\u250\'fan. Fond n\u225\'e1rodn\u233\'e9ho majetku m\u225\'e1 akt\u237\'edva vo v\u253\'fd\u353\'61ke 86 mld., z ktor\u253\'fdch najv\u228\'e4\u269\'0d\u353\'61ia \u269\'0das\u357\'65 je spravovanie podielov v akciov\u253\'fdch spolo\u269\'0dnostiach. Ale prakticky v ni\u269\'0dom nerie\u353\'61i svoju akcion\u225\'e1rsku povinnos\u357\'65 alebo mo\u382\'7enos\u357\'65, preto\u382\'7ee takmer polovica v\u253\'fd\u353\'61ky z t\u253\'fdchto kor\u250\'fan s\u250\'fa vlastne spolo\u269\'0dnosti v konkurze a v \u353\'61tyroch najv\u228\'e4\u269\'0d\u353\'61\u237\'edch, SPP, Elektriza\u269\'0dnej a prenosovej s\u250\'fastave, v Slovensk\u253\'fdch elektr\u225\'e1r\u328\'48ach a v Slovensk\u253\'fdch telekomunik\u225\'e1ci\u225\'e1ch, v ktor\u253\'fdch vlastn\u237\'ed fond hodnotu 45,5 mld. kor\u250\'fan, vlastne je v kompetencii rezortn\u253\'fdch ministerstiev. V \u271\'0fal\u353\'61\u237\'edch sekci\u225\'e1ch, v ktor\u253\'fdch pracuje Fond n\u225\'e1rodn\u233\'e9ho majetku, napr\u237\'edklad v pr\u225\'e1vnej, viac ako polovicu pr\u225\'e1vnych sporov zastupovali extern\u237\'ed pracovn\u237\'edci. V pr\u237\'edprave a realiz\u225\'e1cii projektov rie\u353\'61il sedem spolo\u269\'0dnost\u237\'ed, z ktor\u253\'fdch p\u228\'e4\u357\'65 rie\u353\'61ili extern\u237\'ed pracovn\u237\'edci.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
Fond n\u225\'e1rodn\u233\'e9ho majetku nem\u225\'e1 agendu v podstate a nem\u225\'e1 ani pr\u225\'e1cu. Je to v\u253\'fdborn\u225\'e1 organiz\u225\'e1cia pre t\u253\'fdch \u318\'3eud\u237\'ed, ktor\u237\'ed tam pracuj\u250\'fa a dnes s\u250\'fa u\u382\'7e v poz\u237\'edcii, \u382\'7ee vlastn\u225\'e1 organiz\u225\'e1cia mus\u237\'ed br\u225\'e1ni\u357\'65 svoju existenciu. Vy jej pom\u225\'e1hate t\u253\'fdm, \u382\'7ee napr\u237\'edklad jej h\u318\'3ead\u225\'e1te nov\u250\'fa agendu, ako ste spomenuli, aj z\u225\'e1konom o cenn\u253\'fdch papieroch. K tomu sa zrejme e\u353\'61te v bud\u250\'facnosti vr\u225\'e1time, ale toto je ve\u318\'3emi ne\u353\'61\u357\'65astn\u225\'e1 agenda pre Fond n\u225\'e1rodn\u233\'e9ho majetku.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
