P. Pavlis, poslanec: }{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
\u270\'0eakujem za slovo, p\u225\'e1n predseda. Budem sa sna\u382\'7ei\u357\'65 reagova\u357\'65 na v\u353\'61etky pripomienky, ktor\u233\'e9 som predniesol v mojom pr\u237\'edspevku. Ale vo v\u353\'61etk\u253\'fdch pr\u237\'edspevkoch sa opakuje jedno a to ist\u233\'e9, na to by som spolo\u269\'0dne sn\u225\'e1\u271\'0f odpovedal.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
Vl\u225\'e1da sa zaviazala, \u382\'7ee nebude privatizova\u357\'65. Ale na Fonde n\u225\'e1rodn\u233\'e9ho majetku, \u269\'0do sa t\u253\'fdka privatiz\u225\'e1cie, je len jedna sekcia, ktor\u225\'e1 vykon\u225\'e1va tieto \u269\'0dinnosti, a t\u225\'e1 sekcia m\u225\'e1 7 \u318\'3eud\u237\'ed. Tak\u382\'7ee to, \u382\'7ee fond vykon\u225\'e1va aj in\u233\'e9 \u269\'0dinnosti, sved\u269\'0d\u237\'ed o tom, \u382\'7ee s\u250\'fa tam aj in\u233\'e9 sekcie. A \u269\'0do sa t\u253\'fdka privatiz\u225\'e1cie, je len jedna jedin\u225\'e1 sekcia, ktor\u225\'e1 zamestn\u225\'e1va 7 \u318\'3eud\u237\'ed, ktor\u225\'e1 m\u225\'e1 na starosti privatiz\u225\'e1ciu. Tak\u382\'7ee ke\u271\'0f hovor\u237\'edme o \u250\'faspore 7 \u318\'3eud\u237\'ed pri 110 \u318\'3eu\u271\'0foch, tak je to neporovnate\u318\'3en\u233\'e9.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
Vr\u225\'e1tim sa teraz nasp\u228\'e4\u357\'65 k niektor\u253\'fdm t\u253\'fdm pripomienkam.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
Pani kolegy\u328\'48a Sabolov\u225\'e1 spom\u237\'ednala, \u382\'7ee u\u353\'61etr\u237\'ed sa v \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tnom rozpo\u269\'0dte, ale jedn\u225\'e1 sa naozaj iba o 15 \u318\'3eud\u237\'ed, ktor\u237\'ed s\u250\'fa platen\u237\'ed zo \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tneho rozpo\u269\'0dtu a s\u250\'fa to \u269\'0dlenovia Dozornej rady a \u269\'0dlenovia Prez\u237\'eddia. \u268\'0clenov Prez\u237\'eddia je 9 \u318\'3eud\u237\'ed a 7 \u318\'3eud\u237\'ed v Dozornej rade, kde sed\u237\'ed aj v\u225\'e1\u353\'61 z\u225\'e1stupca z opoz\u237\'edcie.}
