O. Nachtmannov\u225\'e1, poslanky\u328\'48a: }{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
\u270\'0eakujem za slovo. Pani poslanky\u328\'48a, rovnako ako n\u225\'e1vrh z\u225\'e1kona, tak aj va\u353\'61e vyst\u250\'fapenie bolo pln\u233\'e9 rozporov. Na jednej strane apelujete na to, \u382\'7ee by mali ma\u357\'65 \u382\'7eiaci v\u353\'61etci povinne anglick\u253\'fd jazyk. Zd\u244\'f4vod\u328\'48ujete to t\u253\'fdm, aby bol u\u318\'3eah\u269\'0den\u253\'fd pr\u237\'edpadn\u253\'fd prestup medzi \u353\'61kolami. Ale na druhej strane hovor\u237\'edte v \u271\'0fal\u353\'61om paragrafe o tom, \u382\'7ee by ka\u382\'7ed\u225\'e1 \u353\'61kola mala ma\u357\'65 mo\u382\'7enos\u357\'65 vlastn\u233\'e9ho v\u253\'fdberu u\u269\'0debn\u237\'edc a u\u269\'0debn\u253\'fdch materi\u225\'e1lov. Ve\u271\'0f to je zjavn\u253\'fd rozpor. Ako potom bud\u250\'fa \u382\'7eiaci m\u244\'f4c\u357\'65 prestupova\u357\'65 medzi \u353\'61kolami, ke\u271\'0f bud\u250\'fa ma\u357\'65 odli\u353\'61n\u250\'fa b\u225\'e1zu?}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
Z\u225\'e1rove\u328\'48, ke\u271\'0f si pre\u269\'0d\u237\'edtam tento bod, konkr\u233\'e9tne \u8222\'1eza s\u250\'falad s cie\u318\'3emi v\u253\'fdchovy a vzdel\u225\'e1vania zodpoved\u225\'e1 riadite\u318\'3e\u8220\'1c. Jednak nem\u225\'e1 na to kompetenciu pod\u318\'3ea s\u250\'fa\u269\'0dasnej pr\u225\'e1vnej \u250\'fapravy. To po prv\u233\'e9. A po druh\u233\'e9, \u269\'0do ke\u271\'0f to nebude v s\u250\'falade, \u269\'0do potom? Kedy sa na to pr\u237\'edde?}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
\u270\'0ealej \u271\'0fal\u353\'61\u237\'ed rozpor. Na jednej strane apelujete na slobodu, argumenta\u269\'0dne to podporujete pr\u225\'e1ve t\u253\'fdm v\u253\'fdberom u\u269\'0debn\u237\'edc, na druhej strane ale t\u250\'fato slobodu priamo potl\u225\'e1\u269\'0date. Stanoven\u253\'fd v\u253\'fdber angli\u269\'0dtiny. Spr\u225\'e1vne ste poznamenali, nech to rozhodn\u250\'fa rodi\u269\'0dia, samotn\u253\'fd \u382\'7eiak k \u269\'0domu inklinuje. Toto sme tu u\u382\'7e raz mali, raz sme mali povinn\u250\'fa ru\u353\'61tinu a vieme, ak\u253\'fd sme k nej mali vz\u357\'65ah. To ist\u233\'e9 sa m\u244\'f4\u382\'7ee sta\u357\'65 potom s angli\u269\'0dtinou.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
A spomeniem e\u353\'61te jeden rozpor z h\u318\'3eadiska slobody, 20. a 21. bod naria\u271\'0fujete, aby o zdravotne znev\u253\'fdhodnenom \u382\'7eiakovi rozhodovalo centrum \u353\'61peci\u225\'e1lnopedagogick\u233\'e9ho poradenstva. Pre\u269\'0do to nem\u225\'e1 rozhodn\u250\'fa\u357\'65 on s\u225\'e1m? Pre\u269\'0do chceme diskriminova\u357\'65 tohto \u382\'7eiaka v porovnan\u237\'ed so zdrav\u253\'fdm \u382\'7eiakom?}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
\u270\'0eakujem.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30

