\u270\'0eakujem pekne. \u270\'0eakujem, \u382\'7ee ste po\u269\'0d\u250\'favali m\u244\'f4j pr\u237\'edhovor.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
No, pokia\u318\'3e ide o mo\u382\'7enos\u357\'65 kontinu\u225\'e1lneho prechodu zo \u353\'61koly na \u353\'61kolu pri odli\u353\'61n\u253\'fdch u\u269\'0debniciach, samozrejme, \u382\'7ee je to mo\u382\'7en\u233\'e9, ve\u271\'0f na to m\u225\'e1me \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tny \u353\'61kolsk\u253\'fd program. Tie u\u269\'0debnice m\u244\'f4\u382\'7eu by\u357\'65 odli\u353\'61n\u233\'e9 z h\u318\'3eadiska metodiky, ale nem\u244\'f4\u382\'7eu ma\u357\'65 in\u233\'e9 ciele, preto\u382\'7ee musia by\u357\'65 v s\u250\'falade so \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tnym \u353\'61kolsk\u253\'fdm programom. Tak\u382\'7ee toto je absol\u250\'fatne vyrie\u353\'61en\u233\'e9. \u381\'7diaden rozpor. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\loch\f4\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30
